-- Goldman Sachs Is in Final Stage of Study on DFM, ADX Merger, Bayan Reports
-- B y   Z a h r a a   A l k h a l i s i
-- 2010-10-17T04:22:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-17/goldman-sachs-is-in-final-stage-of-study-on-dfm-adx-merger-bayan-reports.html
Goldman Sachs Group Plc is in the
final stages of completing a study to merge the Dubai Financial
Market and the Abu Dhabi Securities Exchange,  Al Bayan  reported,
without saying where it got the information.  Goldman Sachs will present its report to Emirates
Investment Co., which is overseeing the merger, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Zahraa Alkhalisi  in Abu Dhabi at 
 zalkhalisi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
